casebody.data:
Thursday, February 15, 1996

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-2384. State ex rel. Pahler v. Cleveland.

Cuyahoga County, No. 68385. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective February 14,1996.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
